{"tid":2000262,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【多圖】25歲金賢娥落選《PRODUCE 48》 擁姣好身材網民大叫可惜","createTime":"2020-05-03T17:52:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-04T06:22:19.000Z","uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"dd44626299c5a46db890cdba51e5064eb97d7b57","tid":2000262,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T17:52:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4424933/org/819c2bd3d6a30ee13e7dc55ad13f2e4f.jpg/-KJNiFDfMpBtDJBBXNGoyX-_u3OMhx2wVbBhc1WwYXM?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4424933%2Forg%2F819c2bd3d6a30ee13e7dc55ad13f2e4f.jpg%2F-KJNiFDfMpBtDJBBXNGoyX-_u3OMhx2wVbBhc1WwYXM%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=238146a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4424933/org/819c2bd3d6a30ee13e7dc55ad13f2e4f.jpg/-KJNiFDfMpBtDJBBXNGoyX-_u3OMhx2wVbBhc1WwYXM?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4424933%2Forg%2F819c2bd3d6a30ee13e7dc55ad13f2e4f.jpg%2F-KJNiFDfMpBtDJBBXNGoyX-_u3OMhx2wVbBhc1WwYXM%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=238146a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n兩年前，25歲練習生金賢娥（Kim Hyun Ah）因參與選秀節目《PRODUCE 48》而小有名氣，雖然她於節目中落選，女團出道無期，可見她卻因姣好的完美身材成功吸引大眾的視線。現時她主要通過IG與粉絲溝通，不時向大家派福利。<br />\n<br />\n金賢娥雖有着高水準的舞蹈實力，以及標緻的五官，可是在節目中的曝光率奇低，最終以46名止步，無緣以IZ*ONE一員出道。當時已經歷7年練習生生活的她，2017年曾以女團LUX一員出道，可惜並沒有大紅，據說現時正在以DJ身份活動。金賢娥亦非常活躍於IG，不時上傳性感照益粉絲，不少網民看過她的好身材後都表示「沒能以女團出道很可惜」。"},{"pid":"72f00f5ca718df6702859c82c0f99e591fc0211c","tid":2000262,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T17:53:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4424867/org/08572c82fd6d673b56df05a6f1b89b82.jpg/HX6YNujs_7WxcfL3f7hCH8XfKLbjzwi8MlIuazJSLms?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4424867%2Forg%2F08572c82fd6d673b56df05a6f1b89b82.jpg%2FHX6YNujs_7WxcfL3f7hCH8XfKLbjzwi8M